original_title: Only Noise - Las 65:45 horas de gloria de Les Renards
overview: ONLY NOISE is a documentary that tries to rescue from oblivion a tale with Les Renards as protagonists, one of the many bands from the 60s that was a key witness and pioneer in the first big explosion of Uruguayan Rock. It might look like a tale from an ordinary band, but in 1968 this band managed to break a world record.
title: Only Noise - Las 65:45 horas de gloria de Les Renards
